Package: chronometre
Type: Package
Title: A 'chronomètre' or a simple 'stopwatch' 
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2026-01-19
Authors@R: person("Dirk", "Eddelbuettel", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "edd@debian.org")
Description: As a 'chronomètre' is a 'stopwatch', this package offers a simple stopwatch, and
 in particular one that can be shared with Python such that both interpreters operate on
 the same object instance and shown in the demo file.
Suggests: RcppSpdlog, xptr, reticulate
URL: https://github.com/eddelbuettel/chronometre
BugReports: https://github.com/eddelbuettel/chronometre/issues
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
